# areasOfInterest

**Instance Property**

An array of common names of the area in which the place resides.

## Declaration

```swift
areasOfInterest?: string[];
```

## Discussion

For example, the autocompletion results for the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/SearchAutocompleteResult/areasOfInterest] for Golden Gate Park in San Francisco, CA include `["Lindley Meadow", "Golden Gate Park"]`.
